<Algorithm code="             1. Let _proto_ be ? GetPrototypeFromConstructor(_newTarget_, _defaultProto_).             1. Let _obj_ be TypedArrayCreate(_proto_).             1. Assert: _obj_.[[ViewedArrayBuffer]] is *undefined*.             1. Set _obj_.[[TypedArrayName]] to _constructorName_.             1. If _constructorName_ is either *&#34;BigInt64Array&#34;* or *&#34;BigUint64Array&#34;*, set _obj_.[[ContentType]] to ~bigint~.             1. Otherwise, set _obj_.[[ContentType]] to ~number~.             1. If _length_ is not present, then               1. Set _obj_.[[ByteLength]] to 0.               1. Set _obj_.[[ByteOffset]] to 0.               1. Set _obj_.[[ArrayLength]] to 0.             1. Else,               1. Perform ? AllocateTypedArrayBuffer(_obj_, _length_).             1. Return _obj_.           ">
